{"type":"wb","version":2,"source":"https://www.iodraw.com","elements":[{"id":"KFrN95JG6wbMIxpGvea1K","type":"rectangle","x":384,"y":217,"width":1350,"height":883.8181818181818,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#000000","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"sharp","seed":276117676,"version":123,"versionNonce":601774636,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1784078506083,"link":null},{"id":"cOz7qF031UqBEHhf7N8SK","type":"text","x":429.8333333333333,"y":244,"width":141,"height":40,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#000000","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"sharp","seed":1049240236,"version":9,"versionNonce":1782168468,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1784077896483,"link":null,"text":"信息化平台","fontSize":28,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","baseline":30,"containerId":null,"originalText":"信息化平台"},{"id":"wQrn5pb8U-u1lYmP44oTU","type":"text","x":398.83333333333326,"y":294.45454545454544,"width":881,"height":130,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#000000","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"sharp","seed":1095074220,"version":303,"versionNonce":1795414060,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1784079277779,"link":null,"text":"OA平台，信息传播，工作流程的建立\nNC主要是城东各个不同仓库（包括瓶盖、瓶子、包装盒以及手提袋）那边的生成的入库单\nU8主要是财务系统需要审计发来的发票和开具发票\n友空间类似于ERP系统，具有各个经销商的联络方式，还有一个图片审查系统，由销售公司进行使用\n兆信作为二维码专精公司，主要功能有防伪和管理物流信息，后续还有一些酒上面的活动","fontSize":20,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","baseline":125,"containerId":null,"originalText":"OA平台，信息传播，工作流程的建立\nNC主要是城东各个不同仓库（包括瓶盖、瓶子、包装盒以及手提袋）那边的生成的入库单\nU8主要是财务系统需要审计发来的发票和开具发票\n友空间类似于ERP系统，具有各个经销商的联络方式，还有一个图片审查系统，由销售公司进行使用\n兆信作为二维码专精公司，主要功能有防伪和管理物流信息，后续还有一些酒上面的活动"},{"id":"AoV2jyNTv-ySCabNdcMu_","type":"text","x":397.1398601398602,"y":481.3333333333334,"width":1300,"height":332,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#000000","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"sharp","seed":32782124,"version":511,"versionNonce":2028653844,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1784079351133,"link":null,"text":"运行的逻辑是三单匹配（订单，入库单，发票）\n分为俩类，一类是购入方，另一类是销售方\n作为购入方时，物品包括粮食、酒的容器以及促销品等等\n涉及的部门包括采购中心的下订单，由各个仓库收到物品，采购数量核对后，生成入库单，最后由财务部\n完最后的校验，交易达成\n同样，并不是所有都有三个单据都有的，比如销售公司的出差报销，可能是直接发票，中间有个酒店或饭店的消费小票，起到入库单的作用，入库单\n在三单中起到一个核对证明的作用\n作为销售方\n当前公司最大的销售是酒，酒本身不是直接卖给下面门店而是卖给全国的经销商，再分销到各个门店以及饭店\n后续公司为促销，推出“云豆”，本质上也是一种商品，是一种电子商品，要通过发票确定其合法性，通过物流系统对数量精准控制\nOA在中间起到任务信息的传递\n     \n","fontSize":20,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","baseline":327,"containerId":null,"originalText":"运行的逻辑是三单匹配（订单，入库单，发票）\n分为俩类，一类是购入方，另一类是销售方\n作为购入方时，物品包括粮食、酒的容器以及促销品等等\n涉及的部门包括采购中心的下订单，由各个仓库收到物品，采购数量核对后，生成入库单，最后由财务部\n完最后的校验，交易达成\n同样，并不是所有都有三个单据都有的，比如销售公司的出差报销，可能是直接发票，中间有个酒店或饭店的消费小票，起到入库单的作用，入库单\n在三单中起到一个核对证明的作用\n作为销售方\n当前公司最大的销售是酒，酒本身不是直接卖给下面门店而是卖给全国的经销商，再分销到各个门店以及饭店\n后续公司为促销，推出“云豆”，本质上也是一种商品，是一种电子商品，要通过发票确定其合法性，通过物流系统对数量精准控制\nOA在中间起到任务信息的传递\n     \n"},{"id":"5qjiUCrG43IdUZytloLg8","type":"text","x":396.43939393939405,"y":441.4242424242425,"width":281,"height":37,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#000000","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"sharp","seed":780202924,"version":48,"versionNonce":1276115628,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1784078159422,"link":null,"text":"核心逻辑——三单匹配","fontSize":28,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","baseline":30,"containerId":null,"originalText":"核心逻辑——三单匹配"},{"id":"eSyQ93Ls4iYbI4jR9oSzW","type":"text","x":404.3863636363637,"y":772.7861305361306,"width":58,"height":37,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#000000","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"sharp","seed":1064781204,"version":121,"versionNonce":1226574740,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1784079354627,"link":null,"text":"兆信","fontSize":28.45454545454544,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","baseline":30,"containerId":null,"originalText":"兆信"},{"id":"kozbLtp_yI7L7H46br1yk","type":"text","x":398.93181818181836,"y":813.922494172494,"width":1241,"height":52,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#000000","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"sharp","seed":1045997484,"version":378,"versionNonce":408190124,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1784079407521,"link":null,"text":"五码合一，主要想用它解决的问题一个防伪以及串货，当前防伪部分状况是短信发送以及太阳码的方式，物流系统落地仍有一些问题，几个码\n并协调仍有问题","fontSize":20.02932551319649,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","baseline":47,"containerId":null,"originalText":"五码合一，主要想用它解决的问题一个防伪以及串货，当前防伪部分状况是短信发送以及太阳码的方式，物流系统落地仍有一些问题，几个码\n并协调仍有问题"},{"id":"OF_PowTMtLmzd5g6G0tJv","type":"text","x":395.2954545454546,"y":869.1497668997667,"width":197,"height":37,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#000000","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"sharp","seed":389020820,"version":29,"versionNonce":1334728468,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1784079443805,"link":null,"text":"需要解决的问题","fontSize":28,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","baseline":30,"containerId":null,"originalText":"需要解决的问题"},{"id":"MfGAyotQA1tAxrvmxoP34","type":"text","x":395.29545454545456,"y":915.6497668997667,"width":433,"height":52,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#000000","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"sharp","seed":2020955180,"version":83,"versionNonce":1026918676,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1784079619097,"link":null,"text":"发票如何结合“云豆”的生成，是否其具有合法性？\n促销活动，有没有较为成熟的平台，","fontSize":20,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","baseline":47,"containerId":null,"originalText":"发票如何结合“云豆”的生成，是否其具有合法性？\n促销活动，有没有较为成熟的平台，"}],"appState":{"theme":"light","currentChartType":"bar","currentItemBackgroundColor":"transparent","currentItemEndArrowhead":"arrow","currentItemFillStyle":"hachure","currentItemFontFamily":2,"currentItemFontSize":20,"currentItemLinearStrokeSharpness":"round","currentItemOpacity":100,"currentItemRoughness":1,"currentItemStartArrowhead":null,"currentItemStrokeColor":"#000000","currentItemStrokeSharpness":"sharp","currentItemStrokeStyle":"solid","currentItemStrokeWidth":1,"currentItemTextAlign":"left","cursorButton":"up","editingGroupId":null,"elementLocked":false,"elementType":"selection","exportBackground":true,"exportScale":1,"exportEmbedScene":false,"exportWithDarkMode":false,"gridSize":null,"lastPointerDownWith":"mouse","name":"Untitled-2026-07-15-0844","openMenu":null,"previousSelectedElementIds":{"MfGAyotQA1tAxrvmxoP34":true,"pQrnVQWcA_IvPqSqnlkOJ":true},"scrolledOutside":false,"scrollX":21.068181818181756,"scrollY":-252.7406759906759,"selectedElementIds":{},"selectedGroupIds":{},"shouldCacheIgnoreZoom":false,"showStats":false,"viewBackgroundColor":"#ffffff","zenModeEnabled":false,"zoom":{"value":1.1}},"files":{}}